Method 1: Volume Mounting (Temporary)
sudo docker run -it --rm \
  --network host \
  --runtime nvidia \
  --volume /home/nvidia/data:/home
âœ”ï¸ Data persists on Jetson
âŒ Changes outside mounted directory are lost
